window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Paulo Coelho inspired millions around the world and became one of the most beloved storytellers of our time with the international best-selling phenomenon <i>The Alchemist</i>. Now, in the beloved companion to his classic, <i>The Warrior of The Light: A Manual</i> invites us to live out our dreams to embrace the uncertainty of life and to rise to our own unique destiny. In his inimitable style, Paulo Coelho shows listeners how to embark upon the way of the Warrior: the one who appreciates the miracle of being alive, the one who accepts failure, and the one whose quest leads him to become the person he wants to be. </p>"; 
